You can either add the vim runtime to your lua_ls path or disable diagnostics for “undefined-global”. 

The reason why it doesn’t source it by default is performance. 

12:09 The reason why it is “yes” instead of true is because it accepts enum values instead of a boolean. This is the same for other settings like  “backupcopy”.
